      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the grill to high</p><p>Add your <strong>baby plum tomatoes </strong>to a baking tray with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Put the tray under the grill for 7-8 min, or until the tomatoes are starting to blister</p>",
