    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, tear your <strong>baby button mushrooms </strong>and <strong>flat white mushrooms </strong>roughly into the pan</p><p>Season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 2-3 min</p>",
