      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s] </strong>in half</p><p>Add the<strong> brioche halves</strong> to the tray with the tomatoes<strong> </strong>and return the tray to the grill for 2 min further or until they're toasted and the tomatoes have softened</p>",
